race.comment: WESTSIDE BLISS (1) finished well back at this track last time when a 4.5 lengths sixth (18.86) but recorded best time of the card when winning four back. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Has a strong record from this draw, notching two wins and two minor placings from four starts. Worth another chance. TIGGERLONG BINGO (4) has a strong record here with 11 wins and six placings from 22 starts. Hit the frame latest (18.59) when third at this track in a NG. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. BRONTE LEE (2) has been freshened and can sneak into the frame on her best form. Something for the Multiples: TALAKAI (8)
